"application": "STAR",

"software": "STAR (Spliced Transcripts Alignment to a Reference)",

},

"PLACEHOLDER.reverse.paired"
],
"output_files": [
"PLACEHOLDER.map.bam"
],
"command_line_arguments": {
"--runThreadN": 12,
